law.text: The procedures, actions and remedies provided for in KRS 205.710 to 205.800, 403.215, 405.405 to 405.530, and 530.050 shall be in addition to and not in substitution of other proceedings provided by law.
law.history: Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 411, sec. 16, effective July 15, 1988. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 343, sec. 18.
